vfw for Debian/Ubuntu
=====================

1. Install with `apt install ./vfw_<version>_<arch>.deb`.
2. Verify `iptables` and `ipset` are installed.
3. Add at least one SSH allow rule before `vfw enable`.
4. `apt install` does not download mmdb files.
5. `vfw enable`, `vfw reload`, and `vfw refresh` will download or refresh mmdb files on demand when they are missing or outdated.
